Name:Wolf Cub
Desc:The Wolf Cub wakes up with the werewolves and chooses a player to attack with them. The night after a Wolf Cub has died, the werewolves may attack a second target. The wolves will be made aware of a Wolf Cub's death when they wake up if roles are not revealed when a player dies.
